@startuml poster_spiritual_financial
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam titleFontSize 20
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title Lifetime Map: Spiritual & Financial (0–35)

package "Spiritual Formation" {
  [**0–5 Foundation**\nFamily prayers\nGratitude & forgiveness\nChurch attendance\nBible stories] as s1
  [**6–12 Exploration**\nChildren's Bible\nKey verses\nChurch history\nWorld religions] as s2
  [**13–17 Formation**\nTheology discussions\nApologetics & ethics\nVolunteer service] as s3
  [**18–24 Launch**\nIndependent practice\nCompeting worldviews\nMission/service] as s4
  [**25–35 Stewardship**\nExamined convictions\nMentorship of others\nSpiritual leadership] as s5

  s1 -right-> s2
  s2 -right-> s3
  s3 -right-> s4
  s4 -right-> s5
}

package "Financial Development" {
  [**0–5 Foundation**\n529 Plan opened\nUTMA/UGMA opened\nSavings jar\nBrands → businesses] as f1
  [**6–12 Exploration**\nCompound interest\nAccount statements\nStock/Bond/Index\nPaper trading] as f2
  [**13–17 Formation**\nSector research\nPick stocks together\nRoth IRA\nDCA & allocation] as f3
  [**18–24 Launch**\nMarket cycles\nBehavioral finance\nIndependent budget\nCredit literacy] as f4
  [**25–35 Stewardship**\nTax-loss harvesting\nReal estate\nGenerational wealth\nFinancial independence] as f5

  f1 -right-> f2
  f2 -right-> f3
  f3 -right-> f4
  f4 -right-> f5
}

note bottom
  Goal: Not blind belief, not rebellion — an examined faith.
  Don't wait until they have money to teach them about money.
end note

@enduml
